{"tid":1312513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]有咩地方可以做黑警惡行集合？","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:48:37.000Z","uid":99207,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"416035b9747d95ebe97bf972cbc26b62dc36e59d","tid":1312513,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得需要一個平台可以放晒黑警罪證合集<br />\n包括濫暴、擾民、打記者、亂扑人、情緒失控<br />\n<br />\n好多中年、老人家淨係睇到CCTVB播示威者打警察、誤傷記者，但完全無途徑去接觸黑警惡行。<br />\n屋企人甚至連屯門黑警護送廢老、隻揪sir、打記者等經典惡行都聞所未聞<br />\n<br />\n因此想問有咩地方可以收集並整理狗狗啲罪證<br />\n方便大家得閒睇下之餘，又方便各位分享俾家人睇<br />\n<br />\n同時亦方便日後追究黑警責任<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊諗方法將啲珍藏集合埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極需要有效率地廣傳俾啲師奶阿伯知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知現時有冇Telegram Channel專收證據？"},{"pid":"48b8174cc2243c2b6433bb110297e7b8d1226b01","tid":1312513,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:04:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警未有舉旗下放椒<br />\n向街坊舉旗<br />\n無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a4b417e3f4b7fe716b8e39090d23ffee898bba","tid":1312513,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警亂扑後退緊嘅和平示威者<br />\n無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee071b84366b140722785c862d3719525eea7b9","tid":1312513,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警撩人隻揪<br />\n啲師奶阿伯唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efff272659c92b38c5b322b5343914b2a0e35719","tid":1312513,"uid":137532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"tg?